# Private identifiers that must never appear in this public repo.
#
# Usage: copy this to `.forbidden-terms` (gitignored), fill in the real terms,
# then enable the pre-push hook once per clone:
#   git config core.hooksPath .githooks
#
# One term per line; `#` starts a comment. Matching is case-insensitive and
# whole-word. The real terms are intentionally NOT committed here.
#
# example-private-app-name
# another-internal-codename
# some-personal-handle
